Source: libspectrum
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Stuart Brady <sdbrady@ntlworld.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev, libglib2.0-dev, zlib1g-dev, libbz2-dev, libgcrypt11-dev, libaudiofile-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2
Section: libs
Homepage: http://fuse-emulator.sourceforge.net/libspectrum.php
Vcs-Svn: https://fuse-emulator.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/fuse-emulator/trunk/libspectrum
Vcs-Browser: http://fuse-emulator.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/fuse-emulator/trunk/libspectrum/

Package: libspectrum-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libspectrum5 (= ${Source-Version}), libgcrypt11-dev, libglib2.0-dev
Description: ZX Spectrum utility library (development)
 libspectrum is a library which is designed to make the input and
 output of ZX Spectrum emulator files slightly easier than it would be
 otherwise.
 .
 Currently supported are:
 .
  * Snapshots: .z80, .szx, .sna (all read/write), .zxs, .sp, .snp and
    +D snapshots (read only).
  * Tape images: .tzx, .tap, .spc, .sta, and .ltp (read/write) and
    Warajevo .tap, Z80Em and CSW version 1 (read only).
  * Input recordings: .rzx (read/write).
  * Timex cartridges: .dck (read only).
  * IDE hard disk images: .hdf (read/write).
  * Microdrive cartridge images: .mdr (read/write).
 .
 This package contains development files that are needed to compile
 applications which require libspectrum.

